OL,7,FImagine snapping up a cosy, three-
OL,8,Fstorey dwelling in one of Italy's
OL,9,Fcharming rural enclaves for less than
OL,10,Fthe cost of a second-hand scooter,
OL,11,Fwith balconies overlooking an ancient
OL,12,Fcastle and sheep-grazing fields.
OL,14,FUK-based Hussain Ramzan, 31, paid
OL,15,Fjust E10,500 (#9,000) to buy and
OL,16,Frenovate a little old palazzo in the
OL,17,Fhistorical centre of Mussomeli, a
OL,18,Fpicturesque Sicilian town that is
OL,19,Fselling cheap homes to lure foreign
OL,20,Fbuyers and stop depopulation.
OL,3,C'I paid E10,000 for a dream home in
OL,4,CItaly that would have cost #500,000
OL,5,Cin London'
